6/5/2017
Kevin
Mobile


Useful app for Wells Fargo customers


            Being able to deposit checks with this app has been particularly useful after moving to an area with no Wells Fargo around. Wells Fargo has supported Windows phones since Windows Phone 8 and judging by their current response to a screen bug, they're actively trying to keep things up to date. I doubt it's as fast a response as it would be were this an iPhone or Android app, but a first party dev actually keeping track of their Windows Mobile app says a lot about committment to the ecosystem. Five stars for that.
        

