Thanks for the App but it has it's flaws


            As others have stated... when depositing checks the aspect ratio for the photo makes for a lot of dead space and a stretched out preview image.... Although it has processed my deposits without issue. And again to echo others, this latest update created a black screen when opening the app... Only way to fix it.. is to turn phone off and back on (also odd on this update... I received an email maybe a week or so ago from WF asking me to un/reinstall the app 3.0.0 or below in order to update it.. and after doing so checked the app info and the "updated" app installed from the store was the same build 3.0.0 I'd uninstalled... Then I see today it somehow auto updated to 3.1.0 without my doing a thing)... and this black screen issue has only been for maybe the last few days
        

