App works but WP support ends soon


            Decent app. There were glitches before when it came to making deposits but those have been corrected through updates. It does suck that I still have to confirm an access code every time I log in (I mean c'mon really??). Also, I got a message from Wells Fargo saying they will stop supporting mobile version 3.0 and that I need to upgrade to the WP's newest version. Well guess what, there IS no upgrade as of yet. If that's the case, this would be the last straw since I use this app every week for business and personal reasons. I'll likely be shopping for an Android phone very soon.
        

